west germans may be the worlds 
greatest beer lovers but now theyre tops in fruit juice 
consumption too 
according to the bonnbased association of german fruit juice 
industries west germans drank 335 quarts of fruit juice per 
capita in 1987 this represents an 11percent increase over 1986 
and is the highest worldwide 
in second place in national juice consumption is neighboring 
switzerland in 1987 the average swiss drank 296 quarts fruit 
juice drinking in the united states was given as 276 quarts per 
capita 
the west german fruit juice industry had around 165 billion in 
sales last year the association reported 
