an armada of rescue ships and 
helicopters scoured the chilly north sea today for 150 people 
missing after a fire engulfed an oil platform in possibly the worst 
oil rig disaster ever 
occidental petroleum corp the owner of the rig said in a 
statement that a gas leak was apparently to blame derek ellington 
a survivor described hearing a gas leak screaming like a 
