<TEXT>
as michael dukakis looks over his list of 
potential running mates seven names by all indications no one 
of them stands out as an unencumbered choice 
the massachusetts governor is expected to announce his choice 
next week before the opening of the democratic national convention 
where he will be named the partys presidential nominee 
dukakis was on a western campaign swing on thursday scheduled 
to return to boston on sunday aides said he was taking monday off 
but the expectation was he would use that time to go over the 
material gathered by paul brountas the close friend and lawyer who 
has been heading the veep search 
