asked for detailed personal and financial information and each has 
met privately with the governor 
while strong cases can be made for each it often is the 
negatives that play a key role in determining the choice in other 
words it often is as much a process of elimination as of selection 
heres a look at the downside of the seven 
jackson despite a campaign in which he was widely praised for 
