hampshire but then bombed out his japanbashing rhetoric on trade 
was sharply different from the dukakis approach he also was seen 
as too willing to play special interest politics 
hamilton well respected is the term often used to 
describe this senior member of the house foreign affairs committee 
boring is another virtually unknown outside his district 
hamilton couldnt even guarantee dukakis indianas 12 electoral 
votes 
