mount rushmore is not simply a tribute to four men but rather 
is a memorial to the ideas they represent rep tim johnson 
dsd said at a ceremony last year celebrating the 50th 
anniversary of abraham lincolns 66foot face mount rushmore is 
not a place of stoic stone faces its a place of dreams 
