launchings of the new submarinebased missile authorities said 
the 44foot 237million missile carrying a dummy warhead 
package blazed away from a land launch pad at 638 pm edt after 
a flawless countdown and darted quickly into heavy clouds but the 
navy later issued a statement reporting a problem developed during 
firststage flight 
