scheduled to become operational late next year 
the test program began in january 1987 and reeled off nine 
straight successes before logging a failure last january it had 
recorded two more successes before thursday nights malfunction 
each trident 2 is designed to hurl up to 10 nuclear warheads to 
different targets there are to be 24 of the weapons aboard each of 
nine planned trident submarines 
